OL,3,CFarmers' mental health will 'worsen'
OL,4,Cbecause of the Sustainable Farming
OL,5,CScheme
OL,7,FA young farmer from Tregaron has
OL,8,Fraised concerns over the state of
OL,9,Ffarmers' mental health as a result of
OL,10,Fthe plans for the industry.
OL,12,FAmong them, is the which is has given
OL,13,Frise to protests all over the country.
OL,15,FThe consultation on the scheme ends on
OL,16,F7 March.
OL,18,FAccording to 20-year-old Mali Davies,
OL,19,Fwho lost her father to suicide four
OL,20,Fyears ago, the changes could be
OL,21,Fdetrimental to the sector.
