OL,5,CScheme
OL,7,F"I don't want more farmers to be lost
OL,8,Fbecause of No other family needs to go
OL,9,Fthrough what we went through."
OL,11,FSpeaking to the Y Byd ar Bedwar
OL,12,Fprogramme, she said that "mental
OL,13,Fhealth is a huge problem at the
OL,14,Fmoment. I'm afraid the problem is
OL,15,Fgoing to get worse if we go into this
OL,16,Fplan."
OL,18,FOver the past few weeks, thousands of
OL,19,Ffarmers have protested across Wales,
OL,20,Fwith 3,000 voicing their opinion
OL,21,Foutside theast week.
