OL,3,CFarmers' mental health will 'worsen'
OL,4,Cbecause of the Sustainable Farming
OL,5,CScheme
OL,7,FCurrently, the plan expects farmers to
OL,8,Fplant trees on 10% of their land and
OL,9,Fset aside another 10% for nature
OL,10,Fpurposes. There is also no detail on
OL,11,Fexactly how or how much farmers will
OL,12,Fbe paid for joining the scheme.
OL,14,F'Keep farming for Dad's sake'
OL,16,F"I never thought he would do it, I was
OL,17,Fcoming back from school, and then came
OL,18,Fto find him, it was a nightmare."
