OL,5,CScheme
OL,7,FIt's something that worries me, doing
OL,8,Fthings on the farm, and remembering
OL,9,Fthat we always did it with him, so
OL,10,Fdoing it now by myself, it's a little
OL,11,Fpainful, but I want to keep going for
OL,12,Fhim."
OL,14,FAccording to the agricultural mental
OL,15,Fhealth charity, The DPJ Foundation,
OL,16,Fthis February they saw a 72% increase
OL,17,Fin the number of people who were
OL,18,Freferred to their counselling service
OL,19,Fcompared to February the year before.
