OL,5,CScheme
OL,7,FIn an interview on Y Byd ar Bedwar,
OL,8,FRural Affairs Minister, Lesley
OL,9,FGriffiths said: "My heart goes out to
OL,10,FMali. We are making sure that our
OL,11,Fmental health charities are there to
OL,12,Fsupport our farmers and the rural
OL,13,Fcommunities"
OL,15,FSpeaking about the changes to farmers'
OL,16,Flives as a result of the Scheme,
OL,17,FLesley Griffiths said: "Unfortunately
OL,18,Fchange is inevitable for many many
OL,19,Fpeople, not only in the agricultural
OL,20,Findustry, but for many other parts of
OL,21,Fthe economy."
