OL,7,FResponding to a question on whether
OL,8,Fthe Welsh Government will change the
OL,9,Fterms on land use, and if there will
OL,10,Fbe more information about the payment
OL,11,Fsystem: "I don't want to speak before
OL,12,Fthe consultation is finished. It is
OL,13,Fextremely important that we wait to
OL,14,Fhear what people's reaction is.
OL,16,FI know it's extremely frustrating for
OL,17,Ffarmers that they don't know about the
OL,18,Fpayments, but unfortunately this is
OL,19,Fthe nature of how the scheme is
OL,20,Fdesigned with the budget cycle, we
OL,21,Fdon't know what our funding is."
